::DarkMouse::

"Drillbit, KitKat, Stringtra, Quickstrike, Phobia, Scorponok, Myself 
and Commander Megatron. 8 bots all together Commander."

She thought a moment. She walked up to Megatron and leaned upward to 
whisper to him. "Commander, it might be wise to gather more troops or 
build more troops before the attack.  The enemy has us outnumbered at 
the moment."
